Third-party components

The image-to-mesh engine under `layers/image2mesh/engine/` is derived from
pwilkin/trellis.cpp (https://github.com/pwilkin/trellis.cpp), trimmed to a
Vulkan-only build. Upstream carries no license file at the pinned commit; see
`layers/image2mesh/engine/PROVENANCE.md` for the exact commit and the list of
changes.

Model weights are not distributed here. TRELLIS.2 (microsoft/TRELLIS.2-4B) is
MIT-licensed. FLUX.2 [klein] is covered by the FLUX.2 [klein] license from
Black Forest Labs.
